foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: * One BIS FOIA request was improperly recorded in the FY 2007 FOIA Log. The request had been withdrawn on 7/26/07. Therefore, there were 2 pending requests (rather than 3 as previously reported) that carried over from 2007 into 2008.

** The Census FY 2007 FOIA report indicated 8 requests pending at the end of FY2007. However, 2 of those requests were Privacy Act requests that in no way utilized the FOIA. Therefore, those 2 requests are not included in the FY 2008 FOIA report numbers.

*** The National Institute of Standards and Technology FY2007 FOIA report indicated 22 requests pending at the end of FY2007. However, 4 of those requests had been completed in FY2007 and were erroneously reported as pending.
